    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1game_1_1System" kindref="compound">System</ref> that applies scaling to entities based on their ScaleComponent. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This system converts the desired world-space dimensions from ScaleComponent into scale factors relative to the model&apos;s original AABB. It handles unit conversion (e.g., centimeters to meters) based on the ScaleComponent&apos;s unit.</para>
<para>Required components:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>ScaleComponent (desired dimensions and unit)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>ModelAabbComponent (original model bounds)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>TransformComponent (receives scale updates) </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
